# GitHub CLI Configuration

The GitHub CLI is installed at:

```
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe
```

## Usage

When executing `gh` commands, always use the full path:

```powershell
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe <command>
```

## Common Commands

```powershell
# Check authentication
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe auth status

# Create repository
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe repo create <name> --public

# Add topics
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe repo edit <owner>/<repo> --add-topic <topic>

# Create pull request
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe pr create --title "Title" --body "Description"

# View repository
C:\App\gh\bin\gh.exe repo view <owner>/<repo>
```
